VISIBILITY FOR ALL SEA AREAS: MOSTLY MODERATE OR POOR OCCASIONALLY GOOD.
3A. WARNING OF HEAVY SWELL: DEVELOPING ON SOUTHWEST AND WEST COASTS FOR
